(132, 'Politics of Pain series prompts calls for action', 'More than two dozen editorials and columns nationwide responded to our series on the politics behind the opioid epidemic.', '2016-09-28 09:00:00', '0', 0, 0, 'http://news.yahoo.com/politics-pain-series-prompts-calls-090000568.html', '', 4),
